===Noun===
'''chav''' (''plural'' '''chavs''')

#(''British, derogatory'') A member of the [[working class]] in the [[United Kingdom]] who is seen as [[under-educated]]; having poor taste, especially in their choice of clothes, music and modified road vehicles; Believed to have poor social skills.  Associated with drinking low cost alcoholic drinks.

The main feature of Chavs is that they wear clothes made from [[Burberry]], which is a checked material.

